---
title: Loaded Beef Hoagies with Caesar Salad
description: Low on prep time but big on flavour, this 20-minute meal is bound to become your new favourite! Taking a page from beloved diner hoagies, this sandwich combines smoky, delicious pulled beef and veggies with melty cheese, all served with a Caesar salad. Yes please!
